// Three ingredients to responsive webdisign
1. fluid grid: all layout elements are sized in relative unites, such as percentages, instead of absolute units like pixels
2. Flexible images: are also sized in relative unites
3. Media queries: allow us to specify different Css style rules for different browser widths


// Github
1. git init
2. git remote add origin https://github.com/TungPham97/omnifood.git
3. git push -u origin master
4. git checkout -b feature/...
5. git push origin feature/...


// text-align
- text-align property doesn't work only for text it actually does work for all inline or inline block elements and image is one of those inline block elements.
